    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Offered is a concours-level 1994 Toyota Supra Turbo, featuring the iconic 2JZ-GTE 3.0L twin-turbocharged inline-six. This unmodified specimen retains its factory-spec sequential turbocharger plumbing and intercooler efficiency. The Getrag V160 6-speed manual gearbox provides precise gate selection, feeding power through the original Torsen limited-slip differential. The chassis integrity is absolute, with zero oxidation and original double-wishbone suspension components preserved in factory-fresh condition. A true numbers-matching investment for the discerning collector.",
