      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that defines the term 'showroom quality.' This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage and shows absolutely no signs of wear. The exterior features a flawless, deep-gloss factory finish with no swirl marks, stone chips, or door dings; even the undercarriage remains remarkably clean. Inside, the premium leather upholstery is supple and pristine, free of any creasing or fading, and the cabin retains its original new-car scent. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced navigation and driver-assist features, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, the vehicle is beyond reproach, boasting a complete and documented service history exclusively through authorized dealerships. It has recently passed a comprehensive multi-point inspection with flying colors and features a fresh set of high-performance tires. This is a smoke-free, pet-free, and accident-free vehicle that offers a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to own a piece of automotive perfection that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line.",
